# Platform binaries are TRACKED for marketplace distribution (v4.0.4+)
# See CHANGELOG [4.0.4] — bin/harness-* must ship via git clone so the
# plugin works out-of-the-box for users who install via the marketplace.
#
# If you need to update the binaries, run:
#   cd go && bash scripts/build-all.sh
# and commit the resulting bin/harness-{darwin-arm64,darwin-amd64,linux-amd64}.
#
# Only the following build artifacts remain ignored:
harness.exe
harness-native
